title: 598. Reaction to MNF Game + Success of Rookie WRs
itunes:title: 598. Reaction to MNF Game + Success of Rookie WRs
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a special new episode. To start off, the guys break down the Chargers vs. Saints MNF matchup, while focusing on how impressive Chargers QB Justin Herbert has been (:46). Then, the pair look at the Falcons' vacancies at head coach and GM and give insight into what the team should do (18:16). After that, the duo discuss positions that have spent the most time on IR this season and analyze what that tells us (23:38). To wrap up the show, the guys talk about the immediate success of rookie wide receivers from the most recent draft class (26:44).
